extendedInfo.description: Its a simple application  that lets you find the number of touches your phone supports. Just touch the screen to know how many touches your phone can recognize.You can submit your Touch Scores online and see where your device stands in the all new Ranking system.Touch Me to know how many touches i can respond to..keep touching..More updates are under consideration.If you have any suggestion do let us know.Please do give your comments and rating about this app.Version 2.0: Added online Ranking Support.Now you can test how many touches your device recognize and submit that online to see where your device standsVersion 3.0: A new and better look with GUI Overhaul. Added Model Name/Manufacturing Name option in the modified ranking list.Version 4.0 : Modified the ranking section inorder to make it easy to review the results,as more than 250+ Unique Model details are available.Now the ranking system is split to 8 different categories.Version 4.1 : Install/Moving the app to SDCard option enabled. Now you can save your valuable phone memory by moving the app to SDCard,if available.Back key button functionality in the Ranking page modified for redirecting to home page
